name: cornelius
readme:
# Cornelius

  A simple Cohort Visualization library

## Installation

Just include the `css` and `js` files.

## API

You can read the full documentation in <http://restorando.github.io/cornelius>

## Running the tests

* Install dependencies

        $ npm install

* Run the tests

        $ npm test
